Package: dsImaging
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Medical Imaging Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("David", "Sarrat González", , "david.sarrat@isglobal.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Xavier", "Escribà-Montagut", , "xavier.escriba@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")),
      person("Juan R", "González", , "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")))
Description: Server-side DataSHIELD package for medical imaging datasets.
    Provides manifest-based dataset descriptors, resource resolvers for the
    resourcer ecosystem (imaging+dataset:// URLs), and DataSHIELD methods
    for secure imaging dataset management. Integrates with dsFlower for
    federated learning on imaging data.
